'''''Wayfarer''''' was an [[Agave-class picket ship|''Agave''-class picket ship]] in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] [[New Republic Fifth Fleet|Fifth Battle Group]] in [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]]. During the [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] transit to the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]], ''Wayfarer's'' hyperdrive failed and had to be towed to the [[Alland Yards]].

